						<ul class="list check-list">
							<li class="whatIsSynapseText">A <span style="font-weight: bold;">private</span> <g:Image resource='{icons.lockGrey16}' /> or <span style="font-weight: bold;">public</span> <g:Image resource='{icons.globe16}' /> workspace that allows you to <span style="font-weight: bold;">aggregate</span>, <span style="font-weight: bold;">describe</span>, and <span style="font-weight: bold;">share</span> your research.</li>
							<li class="whatIsSynapseText">A tool to improve reproducibility of data intensive science, <span style="font-weight: bold;">recording your progress as you work</span> with tools such as <span style="font-weight: bold;">R</span> and <span style="font-weight: bold;">Python</span>.</li>
							<li class="whatIsSynapseText">A collection of <span style="font-weight: bold;">living research projects</span> you to contribute to <span style="font-weight: bold;">large-scale collaborative solutions</span> to difficult scientific problems.</li>
